  "title": "IT/AV Technician",
  "description": "<h3><strong>  IT/AV Technician</strong></h3>\n<h3>💰 Salary: $2,500 – $2,800</h3>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We’re hiring an IT/AV <strong>Technician</strong> to support IT &amp; Audio-Visual (AV) projects.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Join our team to work on exciting installations and ensure safe, reliable setups for clients.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>What you’ll do:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Install &amp; assemble racks, mounts, brackets, and enclosures</li>\n  <li>Support setup of displays, projectors, video walls &amp; cameras</li>\n  <li>Assist in cable management &amp; housing for IT/AV systems</li>\n  <li>Maintain &amp; troubleshoot cooling systems and mechanical parts</li>\n  <li>Conduct site surveys and ensure safety compliance</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>What we’re looking for:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Min. 1 year experience in mechanical installation (IT/AV/ELV preferred)</li>\n  <li>Able to read technical drawings &amp; use hand/power tools</li>\n  <li>Willing to travel and perform on-site work</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We value every application, but only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. Thank you for considering this opportunity!</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>WeCruit Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0270</p>\n<p>EA Personnel: Tan Soon Hock (Steven) | Registration No. R1109889</p>",
